app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: The following are available online, Figure S1: chromatograms of twelve marker compounds at the detection wavelength of UV 265 nm, Table S1: Intra- and interday precisions of the marker compounds, Table S2: Recoveries of the marker compounds (n = 3), Table S3: Mean contents (mg/g) of the marker compounds in the extracts of the Morus samples, Table S4: The samples of different medicinal parts of Morus alba L.
